						               													<description>Prepare yourself for an eternal adventure unlike any before from an INDEPENDENT Creator.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After the raging magical Tempest Wars scorched the land of Astyria, Nature exacted its revenge upon its people.  For ten years deadly storms, earthquakes and floods ravaged the land.  Those who survived believed the price of indulgences with dark magic was dire - a punishment for exploiting its powers and was known as the Divine Fracture.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Those that survived this horror created kingdoms and religion dedicated to never overuse magic again for selfish gains - setting forth 1000 years of peace, but now a decade later crops are dying and monsters lurking about- a sign that some ancient evil is stirring once more...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Welcome to Oath to Embers A CHOOSE YOUR OWN ADVENTURE with Multiple ending RPG!  It is a world operating out of the husk of myths and legends.  With tons of fantastical scenarios, cavorting characters, and legendary beasts lurking just beyond the safety of civilization, no one adventure is ever the same.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Using a new revolutionary deck building system and combo card system, you must never lose focus. Build your deck to overcome obstacles, slay monsters, and determine the very fate of the world and players around you.  In Oath to Embers, the choice is entirely yours. But be weary&amp;hellip; some decisions&amp;hellip; you can never change. Boernallye needs heroes, but you may have others plans. Either way, will you answer the call?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
